dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Tall Ali section.] Alternate title: Liwa' Karkuk: qada' Karkuk: nahiyat Tall Ali. [Karkuk province: Karkuk district: Tall Ali section.] Relief shown by hachure, form lines, and contour lines at 1 meter intervals. Heights are shown with spot heights. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1937. Tribal lands and land ownership are shown.
